EU Carbon-Trade Program to Raise Air Fares by 40 Euros From 2012, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-04T02:47:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/eu-carbon-trade-program-to-raise-air-fares-by-40-euros-ft-says.html
Air fares could rise by as much as
40 euros a ticket after the European Union’s emissions-trading
plan adds extra costs to airlines from the beginning of 2012,
the Financial Times reported, citing a report by  Standard &
Poor’s .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
